 <span data-ttu-id="4ac8d-105">若要运行前面的代码示例，您需要名为级联样式表 (CSS) `Stylesheet.css`，包含以下代码保存在与网站相同的目录。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4ac8d-105">To run the preceding code example, you need a cascading style sheet (CSS) named `Stylesheet.css`, containing the following code, saved in the same directory as your Web site.</span></span>  
  
